name: Card Readings
description:
There are no questions you need  to ask, in fact, I would prefer if you held the questions only in your heart as this reading is for you only and what  you need to know, usually comes out.

name: Runes
description: Runes have long been used as a divination tool  to bring about clarity and inspiration in you spiritual thinking. A single rune can be used to clarify a simple everyday problem to the most in depth analysis or your spiritual being.

name: The Spiritual Zen Warrior Reading
description:

name: Life Consultations
description:

Using a mix of traditions, intuition and Cards this unique reading will explore what you most need to know at this time in your life, all for your highest good.

name: Distance Reiki Session
description:
Reiki is a Japanese technique for stress reduction and relaxation that also promotes healing. It is administered by "laying on hands"  or at a distance and is based on the idea that an unseen "life force energy" flows through us and is what causes us to be alive. If one's "life force energy" is low, then we are more likely to get sick or feel stress, and if it is high, we are more capable of being happy and healthy.

Distance Reiki is used to send energies over a distance. Time and distance are of  no consequence. 

The person receiving Reiki is likely to feel it happening. If they have an open mind they can usually tell what has been done and when it has been done.

If you believe we are all connected then this is no stretch of the imagination. The benefits with a  distance Reiki session will be similar to a direct hands-on Reiki session.

For this treatment I will need your name and the City you live in.  I would prefer to give the Reiki while you sleep. Please advise of your normal bed time in the notes section at checkout.
